{"tid":1562003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[乖孫入] 寶林眾生相 係時候做乖孫喇！","createTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T16:27:03.000Z","uid":12561,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0cc4db064e3518797360a180dbd294f841297ae5","tid":1562003,"uid":12561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:45.000Z","msg":"話說寶琳站每日都會有免費紅底報紙派<br />\n長期一班老友記會乖乖地排長龍等被洗腦<br />\n一直都覺得好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為就算喺嗰個位置貼文宣都好，都會好快被撕晒<br />\n想比多啲資訊班老友記都冇機會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEaJuLN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEaJuLN.png&h=e883ad3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjCzBq2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjCzBq2.png&h=c058e9e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJRAkSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJRAkSV.png&h=c1f34968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但今日出現一個好有趣嘅畫面<br />\n話說將軍澳嘅中學喺度圍人鏈<br />\n啱啱好就一班老友記同一班年輕人面對面企<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUD7bZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUD7bZR.png&h=691960f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就忽發奇想<br />\n或者咁樣可以係一個好機會比各位巴絲去做吓乖孫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">下次可以揾人幫手同老友記傾幾句<br />\n又可以派下傳單 幫佢地反洗腦一下</span><br />\n<br />\n見到老友記會不斷𥄫下人鏈嘅人<br />\n其實好多老友記都好好奇發生咩事<br />\n所以條洗腦報隊先會一日長過一日<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望各位乖孫多啲關心身邊嘅老友記<br />\n多啲主動向佢地關心一下，傳遞啲正確嘅資訊比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThere are free newspapers giving out to elderly every morning in Po Lam. <br />\nThose newspapers are biased (pro-government) and used by the CCP as means to spread propaganda. <br />\n<br />\nMaybe it&rsquo;s time for us, younger generations, to reach out to the elderly for delivering facts and our cares to them. <br />\n<br />\nWith love, we stand strong. <br />\nWith love, we stay fearless. <br />\nFight for freedom. <br />\nStand with Hong Kong."},{"pid":"9bdc296932a02827391b37e1c69627225a9575df","tid":1562003,"uid":76702,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:03:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34f5b89b55f122c1d27b6a2d5e84d8f487b6f955","tid":1562003,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:04:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b5ac9f3a494700369d690932855cdea3914cf2b7","tid":1562003,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"841b2774ff18b0c4cdd09923804120188663771e","tid":1562003,"uid":12561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:05:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f6928e2e6459dcbac50658f3037311b10e26c52","tid":1562003,"uid":12561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:05:27.000Z","msg":"順便提一提各位，最好裝返個vpn"},{"pid":"8356afe35d859ea6069ff20abda6fd031d342bd3","tid":1562003,"uid":12561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:05:47.000Z","msg":"冇咁易出帖俾狗查到"},{"pid":"7bebce5b0c565d62ea13c088dc4ebd8fba4ce5e8","tid":1562003,"uid":12561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-